Getting Started:

1. Drop the Scribus template files to the Scribus template directory (ex. C:\Users\jolens\AppData\Roaming\Scribus\templates)

	- Kids Logo 2.eps
	- Rounded Title Box.eps
	- template.xml
	- Worksheet Template.png
	- Worksheet Template.sla
	- Worksheet Templatetn.png

2. Launch Scribus and select New from Template > Own Templates > Select your template.

3. At the bottom of the page, write the targeted Core Value for this worksheet/handout.

4. Cut the Main Title box and the Subtitle box.

5. Click Page > Convert to Master Page and name your master page.

6. Undo the cut action of the Main Title box and the Subtitle box.



Adding Multile Pages to the Worksheet

Click Page > Insert and make sure the Master Page selected is the one you made out of the template.